data.description: 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in Pleasant Hill in Bryan minutes from Lake Bryan, Downtown Bryan, and Texas A&M Rellis campus. Open concept floor plan with a spacious living room, large covered patio, dining area, walk-in closets in every bedroom. Enjoy cooking in the gourmet kitchen with granite counters, pantry, stainless /steel appliances and beautiful kitchen cabinets. Primary Bedroom has large walk in closet and the Primary Bedroom has a large tile walk in shower.. Luxury Vinyl plank flooring throughout common areas with carpet in the Bedrooms. The Subdivision also features a Community pool just a short walk from the house.
